==English==
===Proverb===
'''Don't count your chickens before they're hatched'''.
#You shouldn't count on things too soon especially if you don't have them yet.

===Translations===
*Russian:[[не дели шкуру неубитого медведя]] (don't divide the pelt of the bear not yet killed), [[цыплят по осени считают]] (one should count chicks in autumn)

